item.title: CVE-2020-5343|2024-09-17T00:10:31.625Z -- dell -- cpg%20sw
item.description: Dell Client platforms restored using a Dell OS recovery image downloaded before December 20, 2019, may contain an insecure inherited permissions vulnerability. A local authenticated malicious user with low privileges could exploit this vulnerability to gain unauthorized access on the root folder.
